def make_signature(self, http_method, endpoint, timestamp, params):
    message = f"{http_method} {endpoint}\n{timestamp}\n{self.access_key}"
    signature = hmac.new(
        self.secret_key.encode('utf-8'),
        message.encode('utf-8'),
        hashlib.sha256
    ).hexdigest()
    return signature
